      class="p-2 text-center text-3xl font-extrabold text-bot-blue md:text-6xl"
    >
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p class="max-w-xl text-center text-lg">
      Back On Track America (a 501(c)(3) nonprofit, EIN 88-1455899) values your
      privacy. We collect only necessary personal information to provide and
      improve our services. We do not sell, trade, or share your data with third
      parties, except as required by law.<br /><br />
